{"tid":2311693,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"腥港 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-12-04T09:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T03:48:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b39269de6352faa0cacd91691da228fb7257481","tid":2311693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201204/PHQTTIX62FDA5K7GJVUIMRAROA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201204%2FPHQTTIX62FDA5K7GJVUIMRAROA%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=8b5f9398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201204%2FPHQTTIX62FDA5K7GJVUIMRAROA%2F&h=fdc822c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201204/PHQTTIX62FDA5K7GJVUIMRAROA/</a><br />\n<br />\n腥港 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pPAba4oU68SKPL5YFTsul-tpxoU=/917x639/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UNBETWEMSNCZDPTJWOGSQTXVLE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpPAba4oU68SKPL5YFTsul-tpxoU%3D%2F917x639%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUNBETWEMSNCZDPTJWOGSQTXVLE.png&h=24f2655b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前「眾志」三成員黃之鋒、周庭、林朗彥因在去年六月的抗爭活動中因「未經批准非法集結」而分別獲刑，其中獲刑最重的黃之鋒被判入獄13.5個月，三人均不准保釋上訴。<br />\n<br />\n港共政府將香港最優秀的年輕人一個一個送進監獄，旨在磨滅年輕人鬥志，讓香港人及他們的下一代從此噤若寒蟬，不再發表異見。所以，捉年輕人坐監，根本不需要理由。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動始於2019年4月，每一個上街遊行的香港人，包括我，都心知肚明，這是一場沒有大台的自發運動。運動可以一直持續下去，也正因為它沒有大台，300萬巿民自發上街，因共同的信念而堅持。<br />\n<br />\n運動初起時，黃之鋒正重回監獄，在裏面呆了兩個月，為藐視法庭罪服役。我還轉發過他的fb帖文，他為不能陪香港人一起參與這場運動而惆悵。<br />\n<br />\n六月，黃之鋒出獄，走入香港人之中，樹大招風，成為一個爭議性人物。一些不喜歡他的人，因為他呼籲眾人結束集會而杯葛他，甚至有人譏諷他一出獄即抽水。<br />\n<br />\n眾志是不是大台，黃之鋒有沒有人鼓動他人集結，要查清楚，一點都不困難。不過今日的香港，《國安法》取代了《普通法》，「寧枉毋縱」則取代了「寧縱毋枉」。香港，經過一連串血雨腥風的抗爭與打壓，也由香港變成腥臭之港。<br />\n<br />\n執筆日，是周庭生日，「生日快樂」這句話實在說不出口，只盼望所有香港的年輕人仍可擁有他們的明天。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded302ecaa128a42bffe8b5dedbc562b55227a5a","tid":2311693,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a004c65676ae4844dce6185a6d833b9c8749a4a5","tid":2311693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ff3b216130729687ebb51414275d1378096c71","tid":2311693,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\